(5, 1, '2008-09-04 14:02:05', '2008-09-04 21:02:05', '<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/images/2008/08/04/2.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\nRebekka Ehlers was born in Aarhus, Denmark in 1977.\r\nThe majority of her education was obtained at the Danish Art School of Photography, but it also consisted of studies and work periods in London, Copenhagen, and Catena di Villorba. In 2003 she received a scholarship from Fabrica, the benetton research and communications center, where she worked until starting out as a freelance photographer in 2005.\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/images/2008/08/04/3.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/images/2008/08/04/4.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/images/2008/08/04/5.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\nsee more at <a href="http://www.rebekkaehlers.com/">rebekkaehlers.com</a>', 'Rebekka Ehlers for Reef N'' Beef Australian restaurant', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'rebekka-ehlers-for-reef-n-beef-australian-restaurant', '', '', '2009-09-23 15:35:16', '2009-09-23 22:35:16', '', 0, 'http://www.happyphoton.com/?p=5', 0, 'post', '', 0),
