(878, 1, '2009-05-15 05:27:40', '2009-05-15 12:27:40', '<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/53bf_3469772222_0e99f11a12.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<strong>Let me know your background. Name, age, your native city etc. Are you a student? What do you study?</strong>\r\nMy name is Elsie. I am 26 and I live in Springfield, Missouri. I own <a href="http://www.redvelvetart.com">Red Velvet Art</a> and I work as an artist full time.\r\n\r\n<!--more-->\r\n\r\n<strong>Do you remember when you took a camera first time?</strong>\r\nHaha! NO WAY. i was probably a baby.\r\n\r\n<strong>Tell me more about paper dolls. Is it your hobby?</strong>\r\nI made them for my store. I love making toys and art with these characters which represent my best friends!\r\n\r\n<strong>What camera do you use?</strong>\r\nCanon 40d, a little fisheye film camera, and a polaroid.\r\n\r\n<strong>How do you relax?</strong>\r\nI never relax. Ever.\r\n\r\n<strong>What would you change about yourself?</strong>\r\nI wish i had more food in my fridge. i also wish i was more of a robot and i didn''t need to sleep. and i want more tattoos... a lot more.\r\n\r\n<strong>Where is your favorite place in the world?</strong>\r\nCommercial Street. XOXO.\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/0dcc_3483344563_37219c5699.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/4918_3472706870_fba236ca07.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/285b_3470604651_02ef468558.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/3690_1459648447_a43499dd6c.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/1d69_3529079176_db19e2f9ce.jpg" alt="" />\r\n\r\n<img src="http://www.happyphoton.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/05/9b5b_2810823321_156da769a5.jpg" alt="" />\r\n', 'Interview: .elsie*cake., a Flickr user', 0, '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open'